e\": \"新功能\", \"size\": \"M\", \"est_loc\": 400, \"est_files\": 4, \"est_tasks\": 4},\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. CHANGE DIRECTORY AND DOCUMENTATION\n\nAll AR-019 documents live at:\n**`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-019/`**\n\n| File | Status | Description |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| `proposal.md` | **UNFILLED (all TODOs)** | 69 lines, every section is a TODO placeholder. Status checkboxes all unchecked. |\n| `design.md` | **FULLY POPULATED** | 841 lines, comprehensive design with architecture, data structures, API contracts, implementation code samples, testing strategy, deployment considerations, and future changes. |\n| `delta-spec.md` | **FULLY POPULATED** | 276 lines, 6 requirements with Gherkin-style scenarios covering all 4 binaries, build targets, and code quality gates. |\n| `tasks.md` | **FULLY POPULATED** | 240 lines, 9 atomic tasks (T1-T9) with detailed subtasks, dependency graph, and 16 acceptance criteria. |\n\n---\n\n### 3. THE 4 BINARIES (cmd/ directory)\n\n**Directory:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/`\n\n| Binary | Path | Lines | Status | Notes |\n|--------|------|-------|--------|-------|\n| `agentd` | `cmd/agentd/main.go` | 59 lines | **EXISTING, NO CHANGES** | controller-runtime manager + Sandbox reconciler. Uses `ctrl.GetConfigOrDie()`, zap logger. |\n| `picod` | `cmd/picod/main.go` | 15 lines | **EXISTING, NO CHANGES** | Minimal: `ParseFlags()` -> `NewServer()` -> `Run()`. |\n| `workloadmanager` | `cmd/workloadmanager/main.go` | **164 lines** | **NEWLY CREATED** | Full implementation with HTTP API, reconciler, lifecycle manager, graceful shutdown. **EXCEEDS 100-line design gate.** |\n| `workloadmanager` | `cmd/workloadmanager/config.go` | 120 lines | **NEWLY CREATED** | Config struct, `NewDefaultConfig()`, `parseFlags()` with env fallback, `buildKubeConfig()`. |\n| `router` | `cmd/router/main.go` | **74 lines** | **NEWLY CREATED** | Full implementation with informer manager, server, graceful shutdown. **Within 100-line gate.** |\n| `router` | `cmd/router/config.go` | 147 lines | **NEWLY CREATED** | Config struct (18 fields), `NewDefaultConfig()`, `parseFlags()` with env fallback, `buildKubeConfig()`. |\n\n**Total files in cmd/:** 6 files (no `_test.go` files exist).\n\n---\n\n### 4. EXECUTION STAGES (from log files)\n\nThe AR-019 change was processed through 7 stages (ST-0 through ST-6):\n\n| Stage | Log File | What Happened |\n|-------|----------|---------------|\n| **ST-0** | `AR-019_ST-0.log` | Scaffolded the 4 empty template files (proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md, delta-spec.md) with TODO placeholders. |\n| **ST-1** | `AR-019_ST-1.log` | Wrote `proposal.md` -- but the final file on disk is still the empty TODO template (the write may have been reverted or the log shows a different version than what persisted). |\n| **ST-2** | `AR-019_ST-2.log` | Wrote `delta-spec.md` with 6 requirements covering all 4 binaries, build targets, and code quality gates. |\n| **ST-3** | `AR-019_ST-3.log` | Wrote `design.md` with comprehensive 841-line design document including architecture diagrams, data structures, API contracts, full code samples for `main.go` files, flag tables, error handling, testing strategy, and deployment considerations. |\n| **ST-4** | `AR-019_ST-4.log` | Wrote `tasks.md` with 9 atomic tasks (T1-T9), dependency graph, and 16 acceptance criteria. |\n| **ST-5** | (not found as separate log) | Likely implementation stage -- the actual Go source files were created. |\n| **ST-6** | `AR-019_ST-6.log` | **Verification stage.** Produced a verification report. |\n\n---\n\n### 5. VERIFICATION REPORT (ST-6) -- COMPLETED vs DEFERRED\n\nThe verification report from `AR-019_ST-6.log` shows:\n\n#### CLI Binaries -- PASS\n```\n| Binary            | Path                          | Status |\n|-------------------|-------------------------------|--------|\n| agentd            | cmd/agentd/main.go            | PASS   |\n| picod             | cmd/picod/main.go             | PASS   |\n| router            | cmd/router/main.go            | PASS   |\n| workloadmanager   | cmd/workloadmanager/main.go   | PASS   |\n4 binaries confirmed\n```\n\n#### Client-Go Library -- PARTIAL / DEFERRED\nThe verification found significant gaps in the client-go library (which is a dependency of AR-019 but was implemented in a separate change):\n\n| Spec Requirement | Status |\n|-----------------|--------|\n| `Discovery()` method | **MISSING** |\n| `Clientset` embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` | **MISSING** |\n| `NewForConfigAndClient()` | **MISSING** |\n| `NewForConfigOrDie()` | **MISSING** |\n| `New(c rest.Interface)` | **MISSING** |\n| `RESTClient()` in RuntimeV1alpha1Interface | **MISSING** |\n| File path `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | **DEVIATION** -- actual path is `client-go/clientset/clientset.go` (no `versioned/` subdirectory) |\n| `NewForConfig()` | **STUB** -- returns empty `&Clientset{}` (no-op) |\n\n---\n\n### 6. INCOMPLETE / DEFERRED ITEMS\n\n#### 6.1 proposal.md -- NEVER FILLED\nThe file at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-019/proposal.md` still contains all TODO placeholders. Every section (purpose, scope, architecture, impact analysis, alternatives, acceptance criteria) is empty. All three status checkboxes are unchecked:\n- [ ] 提案审查\n- [ ] 实现\n- [ ] 验证\n\n#### 6.2 No Test Files\n**Zero test files exist** in the `cmd/` directory. The tasks.md defines T6 (workloadmanager tests) and T7 (router tests) with 8 test cases each, but none were implemented:\n- No `cmd/workloadmanager/config_test.go`\n- No `cmd/router/config_test.go`\n\n#### 6.3 workloadmanager main.go Exceeds Line Limit\nThe design document specifies a gate of **<= 100 lines** for `main.go` files. The actual `cmd/workloadmanager/main.go` is **164 lines** (64% over the limit). The `cmd/router/main.go` at 74 lines is within the limit.\n\n#### 6.4 Missing Store Initialization in workloadmanager\nThe design document's `main.go` sample (design.md section 4.1) includes `store.Init()` and `store.Storage()` calls, but the actual implementation at `cmd/workloadmanager/main.go` **omits store initialization entirely**. The `ReconcilerDeps` struct is also missing the `Store` field.\n\n#### 6.5 Missing Namespace Scope in workloadmanager\nThe design specifies namespace-scoped informers (`externalversions.WithNamespace(cfg.Namespace)`), but the actual implementation uses unscoped informers (`externalversions.NewSharedInformerFactory(acClientset, 30*time.Second)`).\n\n#### 6.6 Missing `rest` Import in workloadmanager/main.go\nThe `buildKubeConfig` function returns `*rest.Config` but the `rest` package is not imported in `cmd/workloadmanager/main.go` (it is imported in `config.go` which is in the same package, so this compiles, but it is a design deviation from the sample code).\n\n#### 6.7 No Dockerfile or Helm Chart Changes\nThe design document's Phase 4 (Day 4) calls for Dockerfiles and Helm chart templates for `workloadmanager` and `router`. These were not created.\n\n#### 6.8 Known Limitations (from design.md section 9)\nThe design document explicitly lists these known limitations:\n- `router.InformerManager` event handlers are stubs -- dynamic route registration not yet implemented\n- `agentd` has metrics and health probes disabled -- observability gap\n- No mutual TLS between `router` and `picod`\n- `workloadmanager` and `router` share the same store instance -- no isolation\n- Flag parsing uses global `flag` package -- not fully testable in isolation\n\n---\n\n### 7. TASK DEPENDENCY GRAPH (from tasks.md)\n\n```\nT1 (confirm existing binaries) ──────────────────────────────┐\n                                                              │\nT2 (wm config) ──→ T3 (wm main) ──┐                          │\n                                   │                          │\nT4 (router config)